<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Jni on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/jni/</link><description>Recent content in Jni on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/jni/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>[Solution] Java JNI Error — UnsatisfiedLinkError Fix</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/java/jnierror/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/java/jnierror/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="jni-error--unsatisfiedlinkerror-fix"&gt;JNI Error — UnsatisfiedLinkError Fix&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A JNI Error (manifested as &lt;code&gt;UnsatisfiedLinkError&lt;/code&gt;) is thrown when the JVM cannot find or load a native library required by a &lt;code&gt;native&lt;/code&gt; method, or cannot find the native method within the loaded library. This occurs when Java Native Interface (JNI) calls fail.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="description"&gt;Description&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;JNI allows Java code to call and be called by native applications and libraries. When a &lt;code&gt;native&lt;/code&gt; method is declared but the corresponding native implementation cannot be loaded, the JVM throws &lt;code&gt;UnsatisfiedLinkError&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>[Solution] Java UnsatisfiedLinkError — Native Library Fix</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/java/unsatisfiedlinkerror/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/languages/java/unsatisfiedlinkerror/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="unsatisfiedlinkerror--native-library-fix"&gt;UnsatisfiedLinkError — Native Library Fix&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An &lt;code&gt;UnsatisfiedLinkError&lt;/code&gt; is thrown when the JVM cannot find or load a native library required by a &lt;code&gt;native&lt;/code&gt; method, or cannot find the native method within the loaded library. This is a subclass of &lt;code&gt;LinkageError&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="description"&gt;Description&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This error occurs in two scenarios:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Library not found&lt;/strong&gt;: The &lt;code&gt;System.loadLibrary()&lt;/code&gt; or &lt;code&gt;System.load()&lt;/code&gt; call cannot find the native library file (&lt;code&gt;.so&lt;/code&gt; on Linux, &lt;code&gt;.dll&lt;/code&gt; on Windows, &lt;code&gt;.dylib&lt;/code&gt; on macOS).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Method not found&lt;/strong&gt;: The native library is loaded but the JNI method signature does not match the Java declaration.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Common message variants:&lt;/p&gt;</description></item><item><title>New Architecture - Turbo Module error</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/frameworks/react-native/rn-new-architecture-error/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/frameworks/react-native/rn-new-architecture-error/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;The Turbo Module error in React Native&amp;rsquo;s New Architecture occurs when native modules are not properly defined for the new bridgeless architecture. This includes missing Codegen specifications, incompatible native code, or build configuration issues.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Missing or invalid Turbo Module spec file&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Native code not updated for New Architecture&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Codegen not configured correctly in &lt;code&gt;build.gradle&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Legacy native modules used without compatibility layer&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fabric renderer conflicts with existing native components&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define a proper Turbo Module spec:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-typescript" data-lang="typescript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// specs/NativeStorage.ts
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;type&lt;/span&gt; { &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;TurboModule&lt;/span&gt; } &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;from&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;react-native&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;import&lt;/span&gt; { &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;TurboModuleRegistry&lt;/span&gt; } &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;from&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;react-native&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;export&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;interface&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Spec&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;extends&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;TurboModule&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;getItem&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;key&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;string&lt;/span&gt;)&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Promise&lt;/span&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;string&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010"&gt;|&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;null&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;setItem&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;key&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;string&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;value&lt;/span&gt;: &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;string&lt;/span&gt;)&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;Promise&lt;/span&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;void&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;export&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;default&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;TurboModuleRegistry&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;getEnforcing&lt;/span&gt;&amp;lt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;Spec&lt;/span&gt;&amp;gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;Storage&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol start="2"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Enable New Architecture in &lt;code&gt;android/gradle.properties&lt;/code&gt;:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-properties" data-lang="properties"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;newArchEnabled&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;hermesEnabled&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol start="3"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;For iOS, enable in &lt;code&gt;ios/Podfile&lt;/code&gt;:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-ruby" data-lang="ruby"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;:hermes_enabled&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;:fabric_enabled&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol start="4"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Regenerate Codegen after changes:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;cd ios &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;amp;&amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt; pod install
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;cd ../android &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;&amp;amp;&amp;amp;&lt;/span&gt; ./gradlew generateCodegenSchemaFromJavaScript
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;ol start="5"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Check compatibility with existing libraries:&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;npx react-native config | grep -i &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#34;turbo&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Build error with Turbo Module&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&amp;gt; Task :app:generateCodegenSchemaFromJavaScript FAILED
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;Error: TurboModule &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;Storage&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt; was not found.
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;Make sure the native module is properly registered.
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/frameworks/react-native/rn-hermes-error/"&gt;Hermes error&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/frameworks/react-native/rn-linking-error/"&gt;Linking error&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>